    "description": "A Good Place To Die is a casual, roguelite-style third-person action game where you control a hero in a frenetic battle against hordes of zombies in a closed map. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385800/extras/d840e33db53fec0078d02aa7f59e1de6.poster.avif?t=1706696935\" width=598 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385800/extras/d840e33db53fec0078d02aa7f59e1de6.webm?t=1706696935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385800/extras/d840e33db53fec0078d02aa7f59e1de6.mp4?t=1706696935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To follow the development of the game, follow our:<br>Instagram: <br>Youtube: <br><br>With each hit on the zombies you will earn points that are accumulated to upgrade your weapons. You can install and upgrade combat turrets during battle.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385800/extras/fb1bb5ebdb432b9b549d528a9aaccc47.poster.avif?t=1706696935\" width=598 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385800/extras/fb1bb5ebdb432b9b549d528a9aaccc47.webm?t=1706696935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385800/extras/fb1bb5ebdb432b9b549d528a9aaccc47.mp4?t=1706696935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>When injured, look for active water sources on the map to recover your life.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385800/extras/14360485e208cd46c2e1209e1dd2309d.poster.avif?t=1706696935\" width=598 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385800/extras/14360485e208cd46c2e1209e1dd2309d.webm?t=1706696935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385800/extras/14360485e208cd46c2e1209e1dd2309d.mp4?t=1706696935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Every 5 minutes a terrible boss appears and you must face it together with the zombies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385800/extras/e988bed079cdd7dc01cb1a16707173c6.poster.avif?t=1706696935\" width=598 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385800/extras/e988bed079cdd7dc01cb1a16707173c6.webm?t=1706696935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385800/extras/e988bed079cdd7dc01cb1a16707173c6.mp4?t=1706696935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
